#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>gzip</command> is a compression program"
msgstr "<command>gzip</command> on tihendusrakendus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:19
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The gzip kioslave is not directly usable, and is intended for use as a "
#| "filter. For example, the tar kioslave can filter a file through the gzip "
#| "kioslave, in order to display the contents of a <literal role=\"extension"
#| "\">tar.gz</literal> file directly in a &konqueror; window."
msgid ""
"The gzip KIO worker is not directly usable, and is intended for use as a "
"filter. For example, the tar KIO worker can filter a file through the gzip "
"KIO worker, in order to display the contents of a <literal role=\"extension"
"\">tar.gz</literal> file directly in a &konqueror; window."
msgstr ""
"KIO moodulit gzip ei saa vahetult kasutada, see on mõeldud toimima filtrina. "
"Näiteks võib KIO moodul tar filtreerida faili läbi mooduli gzip, et näidata "
"&konqueror;i aknas laiendiga <literal role=\"extension\">tar.gz</literal> "
"faili sisu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you click on a file compressed with a <literal role=\"extension\">gz</"
#| "literal> extension in &konqueror;, this kioslave is used to uncompress it "
#| "and display it as a normal (uncompressed) file."
msgid ""
"If you click on a file compressed with a <literal role=\"extension\">gz</"
"literal> extension in &konqueror;, this KIO worker is used to uncompress it "
"and display it as a normal (uncompressed) file."
msgstr ""
"Kui klõpsad &konqueror;is failil laiendiga <literal role=\"extension\">gz</"
"literal>, kasutatakse seda moodulit faili lahtipakkimiseks ja näitamiseks "
"tavalise (tihendamata) failina."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you are a developer, and would like to use the gzip filter, you can "
#| "find documentation on using kioslaves at <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde."
#| "org\">http://techbase.kde.org</ulink>"
msgid ""
"If you are a developer, and would like to use the gzip filter, you can find "
"documentation on using KIO workers at <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org"
"\">http://techbase.kde.org</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Kui oled arendaja ja soovid kasutada gzip filtrit, leiad dokumentatsiooni "
"KIO moodulite kasutamise kohta ionternetis aadressil <ulink url=\"http://"
"techbase.kde.org\">http://techbase.kde.org</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the manual: <ulink url=\"man:/gzip\">gzip</ulink>."
msgstr "Vaata manuaali: <ulink url=\"man:/gzip\"></ulink>."
